.TH "closure_wait" 9 "closure_wait" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
closure_wait \- add a closure to a waitlist
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" closure_wait
.BI "(struct closure_waitlist *waitlist "  ","
.BI "struct closure *cl "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "waitlist" 12
will own a ref on \fIcl\fP, which will be released when
\fBclosure_wake_up\fP is called on \fIwaitlist\fP.
.IP "cl" 12
closure pointer.
